criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age >= 18 years old;

          -  Pathologically diagnosed lung malignant tumors after surgeries;

          -  Patients with lung surgeries;

          -  Patients with complete medical health records and follow-up visit information (at
             least one follow-up visit);

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients who were not performed with surgeries;

          -  Pathologically diagnosed patients with benign diseases after surgeries;
